<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFCayley1846"><a href="/wiki/Arthur_Cayley" title="Arthur Cayley">Cayley, Arthur</a> (1846), "Sur quelques propriétés des déterminants gauches", <i>Journal für die Reine und Angewandte Mathematik (<a href="/wiki/Crelle%27s_Journal" title="Crelle's Journal">Crelle's Journal</a>),</i> <b>32</b>: 119–123, <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/issn/0075-4102" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/issn/0075-4102" rel="nofollow">0075-4102</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Sur+quelques+propri%C3%A9t%C3%A9s+des+d%C3%A9terminants+gauches&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+f%C3%BCr+die+Reine+und+Angewandte+Mathematik+%28%5B%5BCrelle%27s+Journal%5D%5D%29%2C&amp;rft.aulast=Cayley&amp;rft.aufirst=Arthur&amp;rft.au=Cayley%2C+Arthur&amp;rft.date=1846&amp;rft.volume=32&amp;rft.pages=119%E2%80%93123&amp;rft.issn=0075-4102&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Rotation_matrix"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>; reprinted as article 52 in <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFCayley1889"><a href="/wiki/Arthur_Cayley" title="Arthur Cayley">Cayley, Arthur</a> (1889), <i><a href="http://www.hti.umich.edu/cgi/t/text/pageviewer-idx?c=umhistmath;cc=umhistmath;rgn=full%20text;idno=ABS3153.0001.001;didno=ABS3153.0001.001;view=image;seq=00000349" class="external text" title="http://www.hti.umich.edu/cgi/t/text/pageviewer-idx?c=umhistmath;cc=umhistmath;rgn=full%20text;idno=ABS3153.0001.001;didno=ABS3153.0001.001;view=image;seq=00000349" rel="nofollow">The collected mathematical papers of Arthur Cayley</a></i>, <b>I (1841–1853)</b>, <a href="/wiki/Cambridge_University_Press" title="Cambridge University Press">Cambridge University Press</a>, pp.&#160;332–336<span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.hti.