<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFPrentice1986">Prentice, Michael J. (1986), "Orientation statistics without parametric assumptions", <i>Journal of the Royal Statistical Society. Series B (Methodological)</i> <b>48</b> (2): 214–222, <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/issn/0035-9246" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/issn/0035-9246" rel="nofollow">0035-9246</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Orientation+statistics+without+parametric+assumptions&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+the+Royal+Statistical+Society.+Series+B+%28Methodological%29&amp;rft.aulast=Prentice&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael+J.&amp;rft.au=Prentice%2C+Michael+J.&amp;rft.date=1986&amp;rft.volume=48&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=214%E2%80%93222&amp;rft.issn=0035-9246&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Rotation_matrix"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFShepperd1978">Shepperd, Stanley W. (May–June 1978), "Quaternion from rotation matrix", <i>AIAA Journal of Guidance, Control and Dynamics</i> <b>1</b> (3): 223–224, <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/issn/0731-5090" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/issn/0731-5090" rel="nofollow">0731-5090</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Quaternion+from+rotation+matrix&amp;rft.jtitle=AIAA+Journal+of+Guidance%2C+Control+and+Dynamics&amp;rft.aulast=Shepperd&amp;rft.aufirst=Stanley+W.&amp;rft.au=Shepperd%2C+Stanley+W.&amp;rft.date=May%E2%80%93June+1978&amp;rft.volume=1&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=223%E2%80%93224&amp;rft.issn=0731-5090&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Rotation_matrix"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFShoemake1994">Shoemake, Ken (1994), <a href="http://www.graphicsgems.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.graphicsgems.org/" rel="nofollow">"Euler angle conversion"</a>, in Paul Heckbert, <i>Graphics Gems IV</i>, San Diego: <a href="/wiki/Academic_Press" title="Academic Press">Academic Press</a> Professional, pp.&#160;222–229, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780123361554" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-12-336155-4</a><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.graphicsgems.org/" class="external free" title="http://www.graphicsgems.org/" rel="nofollow">http://www.graphicsgems.org/</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Euler+angle+conversion&amp;rft.atitle=Graphics+Gems+IV&amp;rft.aulast=Shoemake&amp;rft.aufirst=Ken&amp;rft.au=Shoemake%2C+Ken&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B222%E2%80%93229&amp;rft.place=San+Diego&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BAcademic+Press%5D%5D+Professional&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-12-336155-4&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.graphicsgems.org%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Rotation_matrix"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFStuelpnagel1964">Stuelpnagel, John (October 1964), "On the parameterization of the three-dimensional rotation group", <i>SIAM Review</i> <b>6</b> (4): 422–430, <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/issn/0036-1445" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/issn/0036-1445" rel="nofollow">0036-1445</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=On+the+parameterization+of+the+three-dimensional+rotation+group&amp;rft.jtitle=SIAM+Review&amp;rft.aulast=Stuelpnagel&amp;rft.aufirst=John&amp;rft.au=Stuelpnagel%2C+John&amp;rft.date=October+1964&amp;rft.volume=6&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=422%E2%80%93430&amp;rft.issn=0036-1445&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Rotation_matrix"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (Also <a href="http://ntrs.nasa.gov/search.jsp" class="external text" title="http://ntrs.nasa.gov/search.jsp" rel="nofollow">NASA-CR-53568</a>.)</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFVaradarajan1984">Varadarajan, V. S. (1984), <i>Lie Groups, Lie Algebras, and Their Representation</i>, <a href="/wiki/Springer-Verlag" title="Springer-Verlag" class="mw-redirect">Springer</a>, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780387909691" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-387-90969-1</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Lie+Groups%2C+Lie+Algebras%2C+and+Their+Representation&amp;rft.aulast=Varadarajan&amp;rft.aufirst=V.+S.&amp;rft.au=Varadarajan%2C+V.+S.&amp;rft.date=1984&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BSpringer-Verlag%7CSpringer%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-387-90969-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Rotation_matrix"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (<a href="/wiki/Graduate_Texts_in_Mathematics" title="Graduate Texts in Mathematics">GTM</a> 102)</li>
